Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:04.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu Mizuha, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:09.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sosok yang membuatnya tetap hidup\Nbahkan setelah kematiannya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:10.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:13.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi menghilangkan bayangan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan ancaman Nokker,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:20.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi terus bertindak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:25.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin memastikan\Ndunia ini benar-benar damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kita akan hidup,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu perlahan mati di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Firasatku buruk soal ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu tak satu pun dari kalian…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:20.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}abadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi akhirnya aku menciptakan\Ndunia yang damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya aku bisa bersama semua orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:30.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apa kalian akan mati sebelum aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pikirkan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru karena mereka akan pergi kelak,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku harus memastikan semua orang\Nbisa hidup dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kubuktikan kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:44.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia ini adalah surga\Nyang selalu kau inginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang kukatakan, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa membuktikan\Nbahwa dunia ini damai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:52.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kusarankan jangan terlibat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan gadis itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:58.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha adalah keturunan Hayase,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:03:01.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keturunan yang sudah lama\Nmemanfaatkan kekuatan Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya perlu membuktikan pada semuanya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:06.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa dia tidak berbahaya dan berbeda\Ndari mereka yang datang sebelum dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:11.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk melakukan itu, aku harus meluruskan\Nkesalahpahaman Tonari tentang Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:14.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, aku perlu bicara denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tentang sikapmu terhadap kehidupan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti kau terlambat ke sekolah pagi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kurang disiplin sebagai murid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:24.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti kau orang asing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau harus belajar beradaptasi\Ndengan budaya di Yanome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa pelankan suaramu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang berusaha berpikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambutmu juga terlalu panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu melanggar peraturan sekolah.\NPotong rambutmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:37.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya ide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pergi! Kau dengar kataku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa buatkan aku aksesori rambut\Ndengan bulu ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:48.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buat ikat rambut seperti milikmu\Ndan berikan pada Tonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan ide yang buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:53.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini bukti bahwa kami teman baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap Tonari\Njuga bisa berteman dengan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bolehkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika itu membuatmu bahagia…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah dicuci?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:04.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:05.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:09.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku juga akan bergabung\Ndengan klub ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang di Klub Riset Hal Gaib!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini "Klub Sastra Kreatif".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:24.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ambil ini. Aku baru membuatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi memintaku membuatkannya untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Benar, kan?\N- Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak membutuhkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku melakukan sesuatu\Nyang membuatmu membenciku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ini bukan salahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:44.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya jujur tentang perasaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku tidak berniat akur denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha membuatnya khusus untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:54.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku mewarisi darah Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:55.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonari, dia tak bisa memilih\Nlatar belakangnya sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu betapa sakitnya itu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah pembunuh juga mengalir di nadiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi meski kau mengeluh,\Naku masih ingin melindungimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:12.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, hal seperti ini tak bisa dianggap\Nsebagai bukti perdamaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkapan bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anginnya kencang sekali hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:19.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira kau sudah pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah berapa lama kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, Pak Bon mencarimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti Bu Izumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seseorang yang tubuhnya\Ntelah digantikan oleh sosok lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak yakin apakah itu Nokker,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:52.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi "peniru" mengendalikan tubuh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pinjami aku itu.\N- Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya Mimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:55.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahun ini usianya sepuluh tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tinggal dengan orang tua barunya\Ndan kakak tiri, total empat orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarganya tidak menyadari\Nperubahan apa pun padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pergi dan pulang sekolah seperti biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menyelidikinya dengan sangat teliti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia sendiri yang memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau punya fye gadis itu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Izumi membawanya ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kukira kita temukan seseorang\Ndengan situasi yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan ini kebenaran yang ingin kudengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:23.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jika kita menemukan gadis ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu artinya mungkin ada orang lain…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi! Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Gadis Kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa ikut aku sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kakakku mencariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya perlu menunggu di sini, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon, aku akan melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:58.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau tak mau percaya\NNokker masih ada di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jika dia Nokker,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita tak punya pilihan\Nselain menghabisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:04.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau takkan menghentikanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin aku menghentikanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana jika aku salah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena bagaimanapun aku melihatnya…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:18.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:22.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, gadis itu bilang, "Bunuh dia."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tetap tak bisa melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada cara lain…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:44.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:53.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:55.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:59.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjauhlah dari Mimori-ku, Berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa. Ayo lari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:13.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan soal hari ini, Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh. Ke mana orang-orang itu pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tertabrak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:53.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Biar kubawa kau ke rumah sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:54.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak tadi…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Jangan pergi!\N- Fushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, aku kehilangan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak yang kau lihat kemarin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:22.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menggunakan kemampuan yang mirip denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tak tanya Tuan Hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mungkin tahu sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah memanggilnya berkali-kali,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia tidak muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku tidak punya pilihan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- selain mencari sendiri.\N- Hei…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa anak itu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taman Shinonome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:48.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hei, hentikan! Kau akan terluka!\N- Apa ini panti asuhan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau Sosok Hitam, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:15.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lelucon macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuhku terpisah dari permukaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:22.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuberi kau kemampuan untuk terhubung\Nkembali, jadi, kini aku tak punya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menjadi makhluk negeri ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengamati setiap gerakanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengatur tubuh ini\Nagar saat usiaku 15 tahun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tidak akan ingat lagi siapa diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}empat tahun lagi,\Naku akan menjadi manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah mencapai tujuanmu.\NTidak ada lagi yang bisa kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa maksudmu "tercapai"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu aku sudah "dapat" semuanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi masih ada hal-hal\Nyang tidak bisa kubuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti air
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan makhluk yang tidak terlihat\Ndengan mata telanjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku benar-benar\Nsudah membasmi semua Nokker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis kecil bernama Mimori yang kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga melihatnya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:04.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, yang ada di dalam dirinya\Nadalah Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama berabad-abad,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau membasmi Nokker yang dapat terlacak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sisi lain,\Nbeberapa Nokker telah berevolusi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka menjadi sangat kecil,\Nhingga tak ada yang bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker yang kini memasuki dunia ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selain yang kau lihat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak bisa dilacak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memasuki dunia ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:40.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jumlah Nokker telah meningkat\Nmenjadi sangat banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi dan kau…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau juga kesulitan melacak Nokker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi sulit menerima rangsangan\Ndari serangga kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:55.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, makin kecil ukurannya,\Nmakin sulit dideteksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:12:00.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah tahu,\Nkenapa tak melakukan apa pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau ingin hidup sebagai manusia normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bahkan menyuruhku menikmati hidupku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya akan mengabaikan Nokker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, selama beberapa abad terakhir,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:17.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker bisa saja membunuh semua manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:20.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, mereka tak melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker memilih untuk hidup berdampingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya dunia ini damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker bukan lagi ancaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada lagi yang bisa kita lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:43.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya ingin mengabaikan serangga\Nyang merayap di sekitar kita, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Hitam, aku punya pertanyaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada cara untuk membasmi Nokker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang memasuki tubuh manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:51.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa syarat yang dibutuhkan\Nuntuk mengambil alih tubuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada cara untuk membedakannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, apa Nokker\Nsudah mencapai tujuan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi\Nsetelah tubuh diambil alih?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini di luar pengetahuanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menyuruh kami menyerah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan, mengambil alih\Ntubuh seseorang itu salah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:16.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan bahwa tubuh\Nadalah wadah penting bagi manusia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika wadahnya berubah,\Nhatinya juga berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:22.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu wajar. Tak ada yang salah dengan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah hampir waktunya makan malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini konyol! Sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:35.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kalah? Bagaimana dengan Mimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan Bu Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuantar kau pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kugandeng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:41.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk waktu yang lama…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}semua orang…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat menderita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kubuktikan kepadamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:09.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia ini adalah surga\Nyang selalu kau inginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekalahan telak…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengar seluruh percakapanmu, Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:21.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuki, kapan kau tiba di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih punya aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa jika aku memilikimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa banyak yang kau tahu soal ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu Kak Mizuha\Ndan gadis kecil bernama Mimori…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuh mereka diambil alih\Norganisasi jahat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka kita harus menyelamatkan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyelamatkan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menyelamatkan mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau dengar, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada cara untuk melawan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:46.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan bilang sulit menemukan Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana anak itu tahu tentang Mimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dia tahu\Nada Nokker di dalam tubuh gadis itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:03.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain, anak itu punya\Nkekuatan super untuk menemukan musuh,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:06.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi dia bilang\Nmereka tidak bisa dikalahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:12.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa dia mencoba mengatakan\Nbahwa metodemu sebelumnya salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi, kita masih punya\Nkata-kata sebagai senjata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kekuatan tak bisa mengubahnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kata-kata bisa mengubah hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari buat mereka berjanji\Nuntuk tak melakukan hal buruk lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:28.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu, meminta Nokker\Nmeninggalkan tubuh yang dihuni?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:33.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Yang terpenting adalah\Nberdamai dengan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:37.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa mereka bukan tipe\Nyang suka berkomunikasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:38.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu pasti akan berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:42.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa alasannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita coba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau harus berjanji satu hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:54.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:57.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rahasiakan ini dari semua orang di rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:02.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kupikir dunia sudah damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku membawa\Nsemua orang ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:08.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin semua orang\Nmerasakan kedamaian,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tanpa menyadari ancaman ini sampai akhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sungguh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, dengarkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:26.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah, Kuda. Makanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia masih damai hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:39.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Empat tahun lagi,\Naku akan menjadi manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:44.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran alasan Sosok Hitam\Nmenjadi manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:50.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia selalu ingin menjadi manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:53.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, apa itu manusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:57.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku memahami itu,\Nmungkin aku bisa membedakan Nokker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perbedaan antara manusia\Ndan Nokker adalah…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:05.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker jelas kekurangan cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau berpikir begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak punya alasannya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:14.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, jelaskan apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:17.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memeluk dan berciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, hal-hal yang dilakukan Messar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:23.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu berarti Gugu dan Tonari\Ntak punya cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juga memasak dan mencuci pakaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:30.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bersikap baik kepada orang lain\Njuga bentuk cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuda, kau kenyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:36.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ibu Mizuha sangat baik sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga memasak dan mencuci pakaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin bukan begitu…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta adalah rasa kebersamaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:47.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hati yang dipenuhi ketulusan dan kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:51.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar! Cinta tidak berasal dari tindakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:54.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu semua yang berasal dari lubuk hatimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau membicarakan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:00.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak SD tidak akan mengerti\Npercakapan dewasa kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak, jangan memaksakan diri\Nuntuk berpikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kita lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Contohnya, kuda ini\Nmasih belum punya nama, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa saat kau mencintai kuda itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau akan memberinya nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mulai lagi,\Nbicara seperti orang dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:25.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku tidak punya cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:33.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku tidak tahu apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kulakukan untuk semua orang\Nbelum tentu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku sudah melakukan hal baik\Nuntuk semua orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi itu hanya kepuasan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:49.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak peduli aku menjadi siapa atau apa,\Nakankah aku tak pernah mendapatkan cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerti perbedaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cangkang keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisik berkilau.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hanya komponen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatiku selamanya milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:13.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengerti.\NLaut tetap tidak berubah,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:16.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi itu surga yang damai\Nbagi banyak makhluk hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:20.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu hari,\Naku pasti akan mendapatkan cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:25.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa hangat di dalam perutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:33.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa harus menggali lubang\Ndi pasir dengan cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:56.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini "cinta"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizu…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:32.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini keluar sendiri dari tubuhku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yang bertelur?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:36.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:39.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tertawa! Aku tidak boleh bertelur?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mendukungmu, Induk Penyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:49.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu aku di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, itu kebetulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin berjalan-jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:58.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak masuk sekolah kemarin,\Njadi, aku agak kesepian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:00.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, kenapa kau berubah\Nmenjadi penyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:06.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin berpikir dengan santai…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berpikir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin tahu apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:18.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tertawa! Aku serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau ingin tahu tentang cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:24.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingin kau tahu alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tahu tentang cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengajarimu apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf jika aku membuatmu salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bermaksud apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:58.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:03.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mizuha, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:07.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, kau tidak perlu melakukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:13.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf jika aku membuatmu tidak nyaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:15.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan mau membuatmu menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:24.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:26.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:27.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:28.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku menebusnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:30.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melakukan apa pun\Nselama kau tidak menangis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, katakanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:41.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan, "Tolong ajari aku apa itu cinta."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:45.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong ajari aku apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:56.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan senang hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:36.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuh gadis bernama Mimori itu\Ndiambil alih tanpa alasan yang jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.64,0:24:40.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nokker yang bersembunyi di dunia ini
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.73,0:24:44.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengancam kedamaian manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.31,0:24:47.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fushi menghadapi pertempuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.36,0:24:51.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yuki mencoba membujuk musuh\Ndengan kekuatan cinta.
